# Large non-build dirs that overwhelm `vercel dev`'s file watcher (chokidar 4 on macOS)
# → `spawn EBADF` → NO_RESPONSE_FROM_FUNCTION 502. None are part of the web build or
# the serverless functions, so excluding them is safe for dev and deploy.
venv/
experiments/

# Not needed for the web build or serverless functions
docs/
ios/
android/
tools/
*.log
